/2025/01/19/linux-daily/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2025/01/19/linux-daily/</guid> </item> <item> <title>学习日记</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;学习记录&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;希望能（几乎）每天都保持学习，每天都学到一点东西，或者做一点努力。目标是每天的学习工作，能写下至少一句话。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;!!! note &#34;update: 2024-10-31&#34; 能个P，我实在是太懒了&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2024/09/26/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2024/09/26/%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/</guid> </item> <item> <title>example</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Happy new years eve!&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;We hope you are all having fun and wish you all the best for the new year!&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2023/12/31/example/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/blog/2023/12/31/example/</guid> </item> <item> <title>This is my Notes about computer</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;This is my Notes about computer&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Concludes linux, software, latex, etc&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;softwares&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/wiki/code/nvim&#34;&gt;neovim&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2&gt;linux&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;[cheat sheets](/wiki/code/c...&lt;/h2&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/</guid> </item> <item> <title>用btrfs做linux的快照备份</title> <category>arch</category> <description>&lt;h1&gt;btrfs 的备份&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;手动备份&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;转移&lt;code&gt;home&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo rsync -avrh --progress /home/ /mnt/backup/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;timeshift and snapper&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;timeshift 备份根目录&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2&gt;snapper 备份子卷&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;snapp...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/arch/btrfs/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/arch/btrfs/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Index</title> <description></description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/</guid> </item> <item> <title>examples</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;examples&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Text Formatting&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;md- [ ] ==Get==- [-] things- [x] ~~done~~&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;[ ] ==Get==&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[-] things&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;[x] ~~done~~&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;More formatting options for y...&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/examples/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_rss_created.xml">Hiraeth's Wiki</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/cheatsheets/examples/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Index</title> <description></description><link>https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/linux/</link> <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 11:44:29 +0000</pubDate><sou